<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PhotoGraphy</title>
    
    <style>
    
        body,.main {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            font-family: poppins, sans-serif;
            background-color: rgb(66, 128, 243);
        }
        .camimage {
            width: 70%;
            height: auto;
            float: left;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 0px;
        }
        #backGroundImage {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 20px;
            border-top-left-radius: 20px;
        }
		h1 { background-image: linear-gradient(120deg,red)}
        h2 {background-image: linear-gradient(120deg, red)}
       
        
        
        .leftSide {
            width: 30%;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            float: left;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 20px;
            border-top-right-radius: 20px;
			background-image: linear-gradient(120deg, rgb(84, 112, 238) )
        }
        
        button {
            border: 0.5px solid rgb(73, 124, 226);
            width: 18vh;
            height: 6vh;
            border-radius: 200px;
           
            margin-top: 10%;
        }
        a button {
            font-size: large;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: rgb(62, 90, 215);
        }
        button:hover {
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 12px 4px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6),
                inset 0px 0px 12px 4px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        }
        a:link, a:visited {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .image {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
		.head {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6vh;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
		}
        
        
        #ourWork {
            width: 12%;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 2px dotted white;
            border-right: 2px dotted white;
        }
        #firstImage,#secondImage,#thirdImage,#fourthImage {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
        #firstImageName,#secondImageName,#thirdImageName {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6vh;
            font-size: 120%;
            background-image: linear-gradient(120deg, #a1c4fd 0%, #c2e9fb 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 0px;
        }
        .myWork {
            display: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main">
        <div class="leftSide">
            <div>
                <h1 id="titleName">Aravindhan PhotoGraphy</h1>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2 id="titleDescription">PhotoGraphy link your life in many ways</h2>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="#" id="viewWork"><button onclick="document.querySelector('.myWork').style.display='block';"> View Work</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="camimage">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="camera lens"
                id="backGroundImage">
        </div>
    </div>        
		<div class="myWork">
			<div class="head">
				<h2 id="ourWork">My Works</h2>
			</div>
        <div>
            <b>
                <p id="firstImageName">life PhotoGraphy</p>
            </b>
        </div>
        <div class="image">
            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQUyFYA18pyrpph-WWBWAsF02vCpXo4j_hUPw&usqp=CAU" alt="coca cola"
                id="firstImage">
        </div>
        <div class="image">
            <img src="https://sortedmedia.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/DSC0903-scaled.jpg" alt="pancake image"
                id="secondImage">
        </div>
        <div>
            <b>
                <p id="secondImageName">Aerial PhotoGraphy</p>
            </b>
        </div>
        <div class="image">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"
                alt="aerial pic " id="thirdImage">
        </div>
        <div>
            <b>
                <p id="thirdImageName">Abstract PhotoGraphy</p>
            </b>



        </div>
        <div class="image">
            <img src="https://wallpaperaccess.com/full/2748628.jpg" alt="light in a jar" id="fourthImage">
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
